OOC: R. Dahl, Symphony is a HIM, not a HER.  Oh well, I wouldn't doubt
anybody mistaking my characters for the opposite gender, the names can mix
you up.  People have mistaken my characters for the opposite sex before,
they have even roleplayed them like the opposite sex! *Glares at Yanshosh*

::Triggerhappy/Symphony/Orchestra::

        Triggerhappy got up, and fired 3 shots from Blowpipe at Firearm.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
     Symphony tries to think how he can escape from Drag Strip.  But too
late, Symphony's body went flying back as he was hit by Drag Strip.
Symphony quickly got up, and ran out of the way, then he fired 22 machine
gun rounds at Drag Strip, hoping to damage the speeding car.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
       Orchestra nods.

       "Yes, I must have practice in battle!  You, you can be my sparring
partner!" He said.

       Orchestra walked quickly off towards the training room, although he
had no idea where it was.
